name: Luc Valencia
text: Since when did DUdirty governed as de facto ruler of the Davao provinces?  ;-)      Style lang na institutionalize ang tapang?! What do you mean?    No nonsense criminal justice system yet he is also involved in criminal activity i.e., extra judicial killings?  I think there is a conflict of concept here!
